795
00:38:26,458 --> 00:38:27,358
Io come mamma avrei usato quella.

796
00:38:28,860 --> 00:38:35,844
No, altre idee?

797
00:38:38,927 --> 00:38:39,927
La data del loro matrimonio.

798
00:38:40,547 --> 00:38:41,329
